plot: Honey Kisaragi is a perfectly normal beautiful high school student. Until her scientist father is kidnapped by the evil organization Panther Claw, that is. But her father left behind a device she can use to transform into the red-haired sword-wielding heroine Cutey Honey.
opening_theme: "キューティーハニー (Cutey Honey)" by Salia
ending_theme: "泣けちゃうほどせつないけど (Nakechauhodo Setsunaikedo)" by Mayo Okamoto (eps 1-38)
